title: Jason Donovan swaps Ramsey Street for Humber Bridge
text:
Jason Donovan has been enjoying the Autumn sunshine by taking a stroll across the Humber Bridge.
The Australian singer snapped a selfie as he walked across the bridge on Friday. He has been in East Yorkshire appearing at Hull New Theatre in Priscilla Queen of the Desert.
